name: Cafeteria
description: Cafeteria We all love The Odeon's facade on West Broadway in Tribeca, and their signage facing Thomas Street is just as fun. The print is measured at 20" x 16" inches and printed on 100# high quality ink jet paper. Printed by Printicon in NYC. If you are looking for an affordable framing option, I recommend having the piece mounted to a gatorboard. Any print store can do this and it looks great. Basic shipping rates apply: $4.95 - United States $4.00 - Canada $9.00 - Everywhere Else Payments are securely processed using PayPal. All major credit cards are accepted. Each print is shipped in a protective tube.
